The '''Guild Bank''' was an element of the [[Bounty Hunters' Guild/Legends|Bounty Hunters' Guild]] through which transactions were made. The Guild had a 10% handling fee which was deducted from a [[Bounty/Legends|bounty's]] worth before being placed into the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|hunter's]] account.

